      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TENACIOUS DESIGN (7) broke from this box and finished in the placings when a neck second in fast time (22.57) in a Grade 6 at this track. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Has the ability and expected to go close. CROYDON REIGN (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (22.87) at this track. Unbeaten from this box in three starts. Should be about the money. OSCAR INTENTION (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.78) at this track behind Compton Shelly in a Grade 6. Expected to be in the finish again. STORM SISTER (4) in the money here last time and looks a top-three prospect again.",
